              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17051533680731952394">Another block buster from Ashwin. He manages to link historical figure of Chanakya and his Arthashastra with modern day politics. Racy in narrative the climax is delightful and leaves the reader satisfied. The book mirrors the domestic political scenario of India and mirrors it against the dynastic politics of ancient India.</span>

          </span>
